Image useOfflineCompression (cvar)
==================================

Description
-----------

Enables writing a batch file for offline compression of .[DDS](DDS\_(file\_format)) and .[OGG](OGG\_(file\_format)) files.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

`image_useOfflineCompressionÂ [Boolean]`

Parameters
----------

-   [Boolean]
    -   0 - Doesn't write the batch file.
    -   1 - Allows writing the batch file.

