Notes
-----

This CVar by itself is not very useful and has to be used with the [com\_makingBuild](Com\_makingBuild\_(cvar)) CVar and the startbuild and [map](Map\_(console\_command)) console commands. See the [modding](Modding) page for a wholesome use of this CVar.


